node.title: Call for volunteers ends in search for missing doctor David Holland
node.description: Bay of Plenty doctor David Holland, 31, did not show up for work on 11 March after he was believed to have gone swimming.
node.content:
["Police are no longer asking for volunteers to help with further searches for Bay of Plenty doctor David Holland.", "", "
\nPhoto: Supplied/ Police\n
", "The 31-year-old was last seen on 11 March.", "Holland was believed to have gone for a swim at P\u0101p\u0101moa. He later did not show up to work.", "Police said they would continue to investigate any new information recieved on his whereabouts.", "A large search of the beach by 148 community volunteers, plus Surf Life Saving and Costguard members found nothing connecting Holland to the area."]
